#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"A personal loan is an unsecured loan that can be used for almost any "
"purpose. Unlike a mortgage or car loan, personal loans don't require "
"collateral."
msgstr ""
"Pinjaman pribadi adalah pinjaman tanpa jaminan yang dapat digunakan untuk "
"hampir semua tujuan. Berbeda dengan hipotek atau pinjaman mobil, pinjaman "
"pribadi tidak memerlukan agunan."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:338
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Interest rates typically range from 6%% to 36%% APR, depending on your "
"credit score, income, and the lender."
msgstr ""
"Suku bunga biasanya berkisar dari 6%% hingga 36%% APR, tergantung pada skor "
"kredit Anda, pendapatan, dan pemberi pinjaman."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:340
#, python-format
msgid "Excellent credit (750+): 6-10%% APR"
msgstr "Kredit luar biasa (750+): 6-10%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:341
#, python-format
msgid "Good credit (700-749): 10-15%% APR"
msgstr "Kredit bagus (700-749): 10-15%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:342
#, python-format
msgid "Fair credit (650-699): 15-20%% APR"
msgstr "Kredit wajar (650-699): 15-20%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:343
#, python-format
msgid "Poor credit (below 650): 20-36%% APR"
msgstr "Kredit buruk (di bawah 650): 20-36%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:348
msgid "Common Uses for Personal Loans"
msgstr "Penggunaan Umum untuk Pinjaman Pribadi"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:354
msgid "Debt consolidation - combine high-interest debts"
msgstr "Konsolidasi utang - menggabungkan utang berbunga tinggi"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:360
msgid "Home improvements and repairs"
msgstr "Perbaikan dan perbaikan rumah"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:366
msgid "Major purchases or expenses"
msgstr "Pembelian atau pengeluaran besar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:372
msgid "Medical bills and emergencies"
msgstr "Tagihan medis dan keadaan darurat"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:378
msgid "Wedding expenses or special events"
msgstr "Biaya pernikahan atau acara khusus"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:395
msgid ""
"APR (Annual Percentage Rate) includes the interest rate plus any fees, "
"giving you the true cost of borrowing. The interest rate is just the cost of"
" borrowing the principal. Always compare APRs when shopping for loans."
msgstr ""
"APR (Tingkat Persentase Tahunan) mencakup tingkat bunga ditambah biaya apa "
"pun, yang memberi Anda biaya pinjaman sebenarnya. Suku bunga hanyalah biaya "
"peminjaman pokok. Selalu bandingkan APR saat berbelanja pinjaman."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:400
msgid "Can I pay off my loan early?"
msgstr "Bisakah saya melunasi pinjaman saya lebih awal?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:405
msgid ""
"Most personal loans allow early payoff without penalties, but always check "
"your loan agreement. Some lenders charge prepayment penalties. Paying off "
"early can save you significant interest."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar pinjaman pribadi mengizinkan pelunasan lebih awal tanpa "
"penalti, tetapi selalu periksa perjanjian pinjaman Anda. Beberapa pemberi "
"pinjaman membebankan denda pembayaran di muka. Membayar lebih awal dapat "
"menghemat banyak bunga."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:410
msgid "How do I get the best interest rate?"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara mendapatkan tingkat bunga terbaik?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"To get the best rate: 1) Check and improve your credit score, 2) Pay down "
"existing debt, 3) Compare offers from multiple lenders, 4) Consider a "
"shorter loan term, 5) Apply with a co-signer if needed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendapatkan harga terbaik: 1) Periksa dan tingkatkan skor kredit Anda,"
" 2) Bayar utang yang ada, 3) Bandingkan penawaran dari beberapa pemberi "
"pinjaman, 4) Pertimbangkan jangka waktu pinjaman yang lebih pendek, 5) "
"Ajukan permohonan dengan penandatangan bersama jika diperlukan."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:4
