#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"Under the FLSA, non-exempt employees must receive overtime pay for hours "
"worked over 40 in a workweek at a rate not less than 1.5 times their regular"
" pay rate."
msgstr ""
"Berdasarkan FLSA, karyawan yang tidak mendapat pengecualian harus menerima "
"upah lembur untuk jam kerja lebih dari 40 jam dalam satu minggu kerja dengan"
" tarif tidak kurang dari 1,5 kali lipat tarif gaji reguler mereka."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"If your regular rate is $20/hour, your overtime rate is $30/hour (1.5x)."
msgstr ""
"Jika tarif reguler Anda adalah $20/jam, tarif lembur Anda adalah $30/jam "
"(1,5x)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
