#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily fat intake needs based on total calories and macro "
"percentages. Get personalized fat recommendations for your diet."
msgstr ""
"Hitung kebutuhan asupan lemak harian Anda berdasarkan total kalori dan "
"persentase makro. Dapatkan rekomendasi lemak yang dipersonalisasi untuk diet"
" Anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"fat intake calculator, fat calculator, daily fat, fat intake, healthy fats"
msgstr ""
"kalkulator asupan lemak, kalkulator lemak, lemak harian, asupan lemak, lemak"
" sehat"

