#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"A binary calculator is a specialized tool that performs arithmetic "
"operations, bitwise operations, and number system conversions on binary "
"numbers. It supports conversions between binary, decimal, hexadecimal, and "
"octal number systems."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator biner adalah alat khusus yang melakukan operasi aritmatika, "
"operasi bitwise, dan konversi sistem bilangan pada bilangan biner. Ini "
"mendukung konversi antara sistem bilangan biner, desimal, heksadesimal, dan "
"oktal."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:446
msgid ""
"Enter your binary number in the input field, select 'Number Conversion' as "
"the operation, and click Calculate. The calculator will display the decimal "
"equivalent along with hexadecimal and octal conversions."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan bilangan biner Anda di kolom masukan, pilih 'Konversi Angka' "
"sebagai operasinya, dan klik Hitung. Kalkulator akan menampilkan padanan "
"desimal beserta konversi heksadesimal dan oktal."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"Bitwise operations perform logical operations on individual bits of binary "
"numbers. Common operations include AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^), NAND, NOR, and "
"NOT (~). These are fundamental in computer science and digital electronics."
msgstr ""
"Operasi bitwise melakukan operasi logis pada bit individual bilangan biner. "
"Operasi umum meliputi AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^), NAND, NOR, dan NOT (~). Ini "
"adalah hal mendasar dalam ilmu komputer dan elektronik digital."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"Yes! The calculator supports binary addition, subtraction, multiplication, "
"and division. Simply select the arithmetic operation, enter your binary "
"numbers, and get results with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Ya! Kalkulator mendukung penjumlahan, pengurangan, perkalian, dan pembagian "
"biner. Cukup pilih operasi aritmatika, masukkan bilangan biner Anda, dan "
"dapatkan hasil dengan solusi langkah demi langkah."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:462
msgid "What number bases are supported?"
msgstr "Basis nomor apa yang didukung?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"The calculator supports four number bases: Binary (base 2), Decimal (base "
"10), Hexadecimal (base 16), and Octal (base 8). You can input numbers in any"
" base and see results in all bases."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini mendukung empat basis bilangan: Biner (basis 2), Desimal "
"(basis 10), Heksadesimal (basis 16), dan Oktal (basis 8). Anda dapat "
"memasukkan angka di basis mana pun dan melihat hasilnya di semua basis."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:484
msgid "Select the input number base (Binary, Decimal, Hex, or Octal)"
msgstr "Pilih basis bilangan masukan (Biner, Desimal, Hex, atau Oktal)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:485
