#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:114
msgid "What is a factor?"
msgstr "Apa yang dimaksud dengan faktor?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:117
msgid ""
"A factor is a number that divides evenly into another number. For example, "
"factors of 12 are 1, 2, 3, 4, 6, and 12."
msgstr ""
"Faktor adalah suatu bilangan yang dapat membagi bilangan lain secara merata."
" Misalnya faktor dari 12 adalah 1, 2, 3, 4, 6, dan 12."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:122
msgid "What is prime factorization?"
msgstr "Apa itu faktorisasi prima?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:125
msgid ""
"Prime factorization is expressing a number as a product of prime numbers. "
"For example, 12 = 2² × 3."
msgstr ""
"Faktorisasi prima menyatakan suatu bilangan sebagai hasil kali bilangan "
"prima. Misalnya, 12 = 2² × 3."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:130
msgid "What is a prime number?"
msgstr "Apa itu bilangan prima?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:133
msgid ""
"A prime number is a number greater than 1 that has exactly two factors: 1 "
"and itself. Examples: 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13."
msgstr ""
"Bilangan prima adalah bilangan yang lebih besar dari 1 yang mempunyai tepat "
"dua faktor: 1 dan bilangan itu sendiri. Contoh: 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:138
msgid "What is the difference between factors and proper factors?"
msgstr "Apa perbedaan antara faktor dan faktor yang tepat?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:141
msgid ""
"All factors include 1 and the number itself. Proper factors exclude the "
"number itself. For example, proper factors of 12 are 1, 2, 3, 4, and 6 "
"(excluding 12)."
msgstr ""
"Semua faktor mencakup 1 dan bilangan itu sendiri. Faktor yang tepat tidak "
"termasuk bilangan itu sendiri. Misalnya, faktor wajar dari 12 adalah 1, 2, "
"3, 4, dan 6 (tidak termasuk 12)."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:146
msgid "Can I find factors of very large numbers?"
msgstr "Dapatkah saya menemukan faktor yang jumlahnya sangat besar?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:149
msgid ""
"This calculator can handle numbers up to 10,000,000,000. For larger numbers,"
" factorization may take longer or may not be feasible."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini dapat menangani angka hingga 10.000.000.000. Untuk bilangan "
"yang lebih besar, faktorisasi mungkin memakan waktu lebih lama atau mungkin "
"tidak dapat dilakukan."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:172
msgid ""
